snippet: Australian job advertisements in newspapers and on the Internet rose for a third straight month in August to hit a 17-month high, offering hope that a recent spike in unemployment might prove temporary....

headline.print_headline: Australia Job Advertisements at 17 Month High in August-ANZ
headline.main: Australia Job Advertisements at 17 Month High in August-ANZ

lead_paragraph: Australian job advertisements in newspapers and on the Internet rose for a third straight month in August to hit a 17-month high, offering hope that a recent spike in unemployment might prove temporary.
